♪Coming Sun♪

11
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:44,220
=The Gold Behind the Stone=

12
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,940
=Episode 26=

13
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,390
Last time,

14
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,960
I was messed up

15
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,520
by Wei

16
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:58,280
and let him save you two.

17
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:00,240
Today,

18
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,600
how dare you come to me?

19
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:04,790
I have said before,

20
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:06,560
I'm here to beg for peace.

21
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,000
Miss Su,

22
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,400
you don't think

23
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,870
I'm as foolish as that Mrs. Su, do you?

24
00:01:14,660 --> 00:01:15,790
Young Master Chase, you flatter me.

25
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:17,680
There's no Miss Su

26
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,560
in the Su family now.

27
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,480
The three families
that followed the Su family

28
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,480
have already defected to you.

29
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:27,000
The Su family is nearly controlled
by the Chase Rodford family,

30
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,950
with nearly half
of its assets evaporated.

31
00:01:29,310 --> 00:01:30,510
Even this villa

32
00:01:30,730 --> 00:01:32,480
is now yours.

33
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,000
I'm a woman with no home

34
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,510
and no one to rely on,

35
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:37,760
and I've been cheated by others before.

36
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:39,350
Now I realize

37
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:40,840
that kind of bumpkin

38
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,350
can't satisfy my ambitions.

39
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,400
No wonder

40
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:47,040
Mr. Su

41
00:01:47,510 --> 00:01:48,870
thinks highly of you.

42
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:52,350
You're so adaptable
and know what's right.

43
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:55,150
Acquiring the Su family's property

44
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,480
is merely a small lesson

45
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,870
to show other

46
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,680
Huaxia respectable families what happens

47
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,950
when you offend
the Chase Rodford family.

48
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:06,870
You're right.

49
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,680
That's why I'm willing

50
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,910
to apologize on behalf of the Su family

51
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,800
and marry you.

52
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,120
Isn't shamelessness

53
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:18,470
a tradition of the Su family?

54
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,080
There are plenty of people
who want to marry me,

55
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,120
why should I marry you?

56
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,520
I married the Su family

57
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,080
to obtain Ever Realm.

58
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,710
But now the Ever Realm
is about to be mine.

59
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:31,560
What use are you to me?

60
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:39,360
The Chase Rodford family
has power all over the world.

61
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:42,120
Your marriage to a Huaxia family

62
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,470
is just a way to find an agent

63
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,680
who can legitimately

64
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,280
control the Huaxia family.

65
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,520
I, Su Lili,

66
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:51,520
am willing to be your puppet.

67
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,910
What do you want

68
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:57,000
from me?

69
00:02:58,310 --> 00:02:59,800
The antidote to Forgetfulness poison.

70
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,910
You're really doing this
for Wei Jianhao's sake.

71
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:05,150
To save him,

72
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,190
you're even willing

73
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,800
to trade your own feelings.

74
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,560
You've misunderstood.

75
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,150
I didn't do it

76
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,120
to save Wei Jianhao.

77
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,310
It's because of Ever Realm.

78
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,150
Wei Jianhao

79
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,710
has been recognized by Ever Realm
as the domain master.

80
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,360
No one knows

81
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:26,560
how to enter the Ever Realm except him.

82
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,000
If we don't give him the antidote first

83
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,310
and let him restore his memory,

84
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,000
none of us will be able
to obtain the Ever Realm.

85
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,590
You don't have to worry.

86
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,360
You have an expert in the fifth realm.

87
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,120
Even if Wei Jianhao regains his memory,

88
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,150
he's only in the third realm.

89
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,960
Are you afraid you can't deal with him?

90
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,680
It's not too late to kill him

91
00:03:49,710 --> 00:03:52,310
when he opens
the entrance to Ever Realm.

92
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,710
I can't see

93
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,240
that you're actually

94
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:02,310
a ruthless woman.

95
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:04,080
That's why you should

96
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,520
choose me to be
the Chase Rodford family's puppet.

97
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:12,120
I'll consider your proposal.

98
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,060
Someone, go take Miss Lili

99
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:16,390
to her room to rest.

100
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,870
What are you doing here?

101
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,600
Do you want to see me
make a fool of myself?

102
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,800
Su Lili,

103
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,950
don't get too cocky.

104
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,480
With my Brother Bai around,

105
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,720
you can't take over

106
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,950
the Su family so easily.

107
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:00,030
Aunt Bai,

108
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,830
you're hopelessly stupid.

109
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,900
What are you talking about?

110
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,120
Can't you see

111
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,800
that Young Master Chase is using you?

112
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,240
Stop trying to fool me.

113
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,750
If you hadn't interfered,

114
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,760
Young Master Chase

115
00:05:12,770 --> 00:05:14,190
would have married our Wan'er.

116
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:18,000
Do you really think
he wants to marry the Su family?

117
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:19,920
He's just using you.

118
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
His real intention

119
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:23,070
is to seize the Su family's assets.

120
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,360
He took advantage of your greed,

121
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,600
your ignorance, and your vanity,

122
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,570
and collaborated with you

123
00:05:27,570 --> 00:05:29,190
to enter the Su family
to poison Grandpa,

124
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:30,940
and then tried to encroach
on the Su family.

125
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,680
Now that you have no more use for him,

126
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,120
he'll immediately leave you behind.

127
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,750
You're still fantasizing about him?

128
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,000
The Chase Rodford family

129
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:40,600
has assets all over the world,

130
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,600
so why would they

131
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,480
care about the Su family?

132
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,430
The Su family's wealth

133
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,750
is nothing to him.

134
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,360
His true intention

135
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,120
is to get the Jade Street
that the Su family stole,

136
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:55,190
where the Ever Realm is hidden.

137
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:56,750
He's after the Ever Realm?

138
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,160
But so what?

139
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:00,850
Who wouldn't want to get the Ever Realm,

140
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,040
let alone

141
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,920
a top consortium
like the Chase Rodford family?

142
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,250
As long as we two families

143
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:08,560
form an alliance through marriage,

144
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:09,670
the Ever Realm

145
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,430
will be our Su family's too.

146
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:15,160
Once the Ever Realm falls
into the hands of someone

147
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,220
with a bad heart
like Young Master Chase,

148
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,560
it won't just be the Su family
that's usurped,

149
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,720
but also other families in Huaxia.

150
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,460
Even your maternal Bai family

151
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,600
will suffer and be completely

152
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,750
controlled by him.

153
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,190
This... this is impossible.

154
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,310
Impossible!

155
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,800
The only one who can stop
the Chase Rodford family

156
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,160
and save the Su family

157
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:35,750
is Wei Jianhao,
whom you've always despised.

158
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,750
That kid?

159
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,800
What can he do

160
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,310
against Young Master Chase?

161
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,270
He's now the Master of Ever Realm.

162
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,560
Of course, he can.

163
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,600
If it weren't for Wan'er,

164
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,360
I wouldn't even bother telling you this.

165
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,560
Think about it yourself.

166
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,000
Am I

167
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,120
really wrong?

168
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:32,310
My dear,

169
00:07:35,530 --> 00:07:36,510
if only you could be held

170
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,920
in my arms all the time

171
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,560
like the pillow Sister gave me.

172
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,480
Xia Changyin said

173
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,310
Qing'er fled back to the Ye family

174
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:56,360
to save her life.

175
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,000
I don't believe it.

176
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:02,270
I know

177
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:05,070
the Ye family treated her badly.

178
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,720
She wouldn't leave you here.

179
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,680
Qing'er must have gone back

180
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,680
to think of a way out, just like Sister.

181
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:28,800
Sister went back to the villa
to look for Young Master Chase alone.

182
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,120
I'm worried.

183
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:36,510
Young Master Chase is a playboy

184
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,150
and a philanderer.

185
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,390
I don't know what he'll do to Sister.

186
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:52,550
I know.

187
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,150
You liked

188
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:04,510
Sister before.

189
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,600
Don't worry.

190
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,670
I'll bring her back.

191
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,750
So we can still

192
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,550
be together

193
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,960
like before.

194
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,280
Cousin...

195
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,560
Cousin,

196
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:13,910
what are you doing here?

197
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,320
Why are you alone?

198
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,320
Where is that Wei Jianhao?

199
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,230
What do you

200
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,200
want to do?

201
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,120
Don't be nervous.

202
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,150
I'm not here to fight.

203
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:36,720
The antidote to Forgetfulness poison.

204
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,440
Antidote?

205
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,360
How did you get it?

206
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:44,790
Lili gave it to me.

207
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,320
I really feel sorry for Lili.

208
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:50,870
What kind of trickery did he use

209
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,270
to make her sacrifice so much for him?

210
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,910
What happened to Sister?

211
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:56,870
Don't you know?

212
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,750
Lili traded her engagement

213
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:03,030
with Young Master Chase

214
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,120
for the antidote.

215
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,280
Sister...

216
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:09,750
How could she

217
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:12,080
agree to marry Young Master Chase?

218
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,360
Wasn't it all for Wei Jianhao?

219
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:16,360
Why else would Young Master Chase
give us the antidote?

220
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:20,790
Lili even promised

221
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,200
to take the Su family

222
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,140
to defect to Young Master Chase.

223
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:28,920
So,

224
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,200
you take the antidote

225
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:33,220
that Lili traded herself
and the Su family for

226
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,480
and give it to that loser.

227
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,160
By the way, tell him

228
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,790
I received a wedding invitation
from the Ye family.

229
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,470
It seems the Ye family

230
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,550
is having a wedding too.

231
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,030
What wedding?

232
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:45,630
The current head of Su family,
Fourth Master, is getting married.

233
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
He's marrying

234
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:48,720
the Ye family's granddaughter,
Ye Qing'er.

235
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,510
Fourth uncle?

236
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,320
Isn't he a fool?

237
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,200
How can he be the new head

238
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,120
and marry Qing'er?

239
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,320
Grandpa promised me

240
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,840
that this marriage wouldn't count.

241
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:02,180
The one in charge
of the Su family now is not Mr. Su,

242
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,100
but Young Master Chase.

243
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,750
Of course, he wants to make a fool
be the head of Su family,

244
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,960
so he can control it easily.

245
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:11,350
In order for the Ye family

246
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,670
to defect to Young Master Chase,

247
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,440
they sent Ye Qing'er out

248
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,680
as a gift to celebrate
the new head's appointment.

249
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:23,670
It's useless to tell you now.

250
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,390
I shouldn't expect a loser

251
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:26,750
who has to rely on a woman

252
00:12:27,290 --> 00:12:28,150
to save him

253
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:29,750
to be able to protect Lili.

254
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,960
Who says I can't?

255
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,750
My dear,

256
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,440
you've finally woken up.

257
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:12,120
How can you protect others

258
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:13,680
with this pathetic look?

259
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:16,920
Young Master Bai,

260
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:20,030
you have to trust me.

261
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:22,720
You...

262
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,550
Don't imitate me.

263
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,960
My dear,

264
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,630
you've remembered everything?

265
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:37,960
Wei Jianhao,

266
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:39,620
you've had enough

267
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:41,930
of living off others
and want to be a dignified man, right?

268
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,110
Fine,

269
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,960
then go and rescue Lili.

270
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,720
But don't blame me for not warning you.

271
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:49,450
Even if your memory's back,

272
00:13:49,450 --> 00:13:50,320
what can you do?

273
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,030
You're in the third realm,

274
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:53,790
and you want to challenge
the fifth realm?

275
00:13:54,790 --> 00:13:55,960
Don't be so presumptuous.

276
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,200
My dear,

277
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:12,960
do you really remember everything?

278
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,390
(Now that I think about it,)

279
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:25,230
(it should be Black Tortoise)

280
00:14:25,230 --> 00:14:27,270
(who helped me with the help
of those stones in the basement.)

281
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:38,110
Sister Wan'er,

282
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,510
your injury...

283
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,600
Just a minor injury.

